    <thetext>The JDK8 compiler accepts this cast but Eclipse JDK8 does not:

package junk;

public class Junk4 {
    private void setValue(Number n) {
        int rounded = (int) Math.round((double) n);
    }
}

I expect other casts such as (float) and (int) should be accepted.</thetext>
